msgstr "**Hoek in graden vanuit de originele lijn op de punten**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7307
msgid "Default: 90.0"
msgstr "Standaard: 90.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7308
